{
  "stem": "4184.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They did not want to take chances in keeping people in places too long.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Even some time I was told that I have to take a train ride, I remember once, to Toulouse.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they told me to try to sit with Germans if you can.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They have these compartments on a train, and if you see an empty seat in a compartment where there are Germans in there, just go in there and sit and, kind of, listen what they have to say.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Apparently there were certain areas where the underground wanted to know things-- maybe where they were going or about the soldiers.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I used to do that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, they didn't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had my French papers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the underground, what they do to you, they give you a whole new birth certificate, a whole new identification card, and they drill you.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You have to, sort of, block out your past life.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You are now-- my name was changed to Florence Suzanne Van Sant.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they really work with you because if, God forbid, the French looked at your papers and-- I was more worried about the French looking at my papers than the Germans.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The Germans didn't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They saw my papers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They didn't pay any attention They didn't know [? whether they were ?] real or false.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was-- we were more afraid of the French government, the pro-German, the Vichy government.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But so far, I had lucked out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You know, I had no problem.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, you really never get to know the people for real because they really don't-- you're not supposed to know so much about their name.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because if, God forbid, you get caught, and they will say, who gave you these papers?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know these papers are not right.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
